
This application is intended for user interface design.
Your support Android 2.2 and above.

About the application

Kontiki is an application that will try to motivate users to read several books 
or other reading material, by adding to reading content. 
This involves storing user stats, connection to social media, 
user reviews and news flow in a single application. 
By applying to judge the interactivity between users of the application, 
we hope that it will be more exciting a read books, 
but not least easier to find books they like and the option of 
discussing the books you've read with others.


Feel free to join or comment